rength and muscle building, check out\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\/pmc\/articles\/PMC3879660\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">this review<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Contrary to mythos, there is not an &#8220;anabolic window&#8221; in which you have to chug a protein shake immediately after a workout. In truth, it&#8217;s total protein consumption throughout the day and generally getting enough protein within the several hours around your workout that matters. After that, consistency and commitment should be applied to an &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/thefitness.wiki\/faq\/how-important-is-nutrient-or-meal-timing\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">How important is nutrient or meal timing?<\/span> <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":143553630,"featured_media":0,"parent":18,"menu_order":24,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"advanced_seo_description":"","spay_email":""},"jetpack_likes_enabled":false,"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/PabVqD-31","jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":11,"url":"https:\/\/thefitness.wiki\/adding-physical-activity\/","url_meta":{"origin":187,"position":0},"title":"Adding Physical Activity","date":"August 20, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Training, or Exercising? When adding physical activity to your life, it's important to first get clear on whether you want to\u00a0exercise\u00a0or\u00a0train.\u00a0Mark Rippetoe explains the difference very well: Exercise is physical activity performed for the effect it produces today \u2014 right now. [...] Exercise is physical activity done for its own\u2026","rel":"","context":"Similar post","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39,"url":"https:\/\/thefitness.wiki\/routines\/r-fitness-basic-beginner-routine\/","url_meta":{"origin":187,"position":1},